title: Cant log in :(
body:
Wtf why do i get log in error when i log in on eune but when i log in on euw it works fine, i dont get it... 

Euw > Eune confirmed?

replies.body:
I don't think anyone has sufficient evidence that EUW > EUNE. However, we're aware of the EUNE login issues and are currently addressing them on the EU boards and are updating the post as we get more information. [Here](http://boards.eune.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support-en/vIIOYAMo-updated-1648-03-07-16-eune-login-issues-02-07-16) is where you can find the post.

Let me know if you have any questions.
